## âš ï¸ Anti-Patterns

| âŒ NEVER | âœ… ALWAYS | Why |
|---------|-----------|-----|
| `@apply` everywhere | Inline utility classes | @apply increases CSS bundle size |
| Arbitrary values like `w-[137px]` | Design tokens | Hard to maintain, inconsistent |
| `!important` in utilities | Proper specificity order | Indicates specificity problem |
| Not using responsive variants | Mobile-first approach | `md:`, `lg:` breakpoints |
| Hardcoding colors | Theme colors | Consistent theming |
| Inline styles | Tailwind classes | Defeats utility-first purpose |

